    "title": "Property Consultant - Select CityWalk South Asia Partners - Multiple Openings",
    "description": "We at Select CityWalk South Asia Partners are looking for an experienced Property Consultant based out of Ghaziabad. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout Select CityWalk South Asia Partners:\nSelect CityWalk South Asia Partners is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Conduct site visits and property presentations for clients\n• Conduct land acquisition due diligence and feasibility studies\n• Source and close property deals with prospective buyers and investors\n• Maintain a pipeline of qualified leads using CRM software\n• Conduct market research and provide competitive analysis\n• Coordinate with legal teams for documentation and title verification\n• Build relationships with channel partners and brokers\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• CA / CMA / CFA certification\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in MS Office\n• Proficiency in Sales Techniques\n• Proficiency in Market Research\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in Lease Administration\n• Proficiency in Property Valuation\n• Proficiency in Financial Modeling\n• Proficiency in Negotiation Skills\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Ghaziabad, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Select CityWalk South Asia Partners!",
